<H4>    Khieu Samphan Replies to Sihanouk </H4>

<F P=102> BK2804135394 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 1300 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2804135394 </F>
<F P=104>  Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
