  [Text] On 25 April, our forces attacked a company position 
of the communist Vietnamese puppets and totally liberated 
Kompong Chrey township in Kirivong District of Takeo Province. 
We killed three enemy soldiers, including a major, and wounded 
a first lieutenant; destroyed two military trucks and two 
military motorcycles; and seized five AK rifles, a 
drum-magazined machine gun, a pistol, and a quantity of 
ammunition and war materiel. 

