<H3> <TI>   Foundation Formed To Promote Small Businesses </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foundation Formed To Promote Small Businesses </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2904074594 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 0534 GMT 29 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2904074594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 28 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- Such 
foundation has been established by the Ministry of Nature and 
Environment of Mongolia in cooperation with the UNO [United 
Nations Organization] development programme. The foundation for 
promoting small businesses is intended for improving the living 
standard and cultural level of the people residing on the 
territory of the preserved areas. The world ecological fund has 
provided the foundation for promoting small businesses some 75 
thousand USd [U.S. dollars]. 

</TEXT>

